rr # Graphiques draw_g <- function(value = _mean) { ggplot(data = wdbc) + aes_string(x = value, fill = ) + geom_density(adjust = 1) + theme_minimal() + theme(legend.position = ‘none’) } lapply(features, draw_g) -> a plot_grid(plotlist = a)
